title: Does anyone have more upvotes than "Laughing Fish" ?

replies.body: {{champion:267}} He is a God amongst us mere mortals. Praise be unto him.
I honestly don't know, but I'd guess it's unlikely. Laughing Fish is a legend, and for good reason.
Yeah it is unlikely, they couldnâ€™t really go unseen as they would have to be pretty active. One can only achieve such an amount through relentless spamming lol

No. I have the most on the boards I am 99% sure. If anyone has more I have not seen it, but I doubt they would considering the only reason I have so much is due to the high frequency I used to make meme threads. In order to have this much someone would need to post a LOT

Malicious Metal is up there with 122.5k. Considering how most of that isn't from Memes and Games, I think that's pretty impressive.

Most of the other usual suspects I can think of are in the 50-60k range.

Yeah MM is up there.. He is most like the most consistent one at gathering upvotes. 

Still a ways off though, I recently hit 210k
